<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>1329</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ gào sù wǒ tā zhī dào wǒ de xū yào zhǔ gào sù wǒ tā zhī dào wǒ de xū yào
 wǒ de tàn xī tā dōu tīng dào jīng lì de tòng kǔ dōu shì wèi wǒ hǎo
 tā dōu juàn gù tiān kōng fēi xiáng de xiǎo niǎo tā gèng juàn gù wǒ yīn wǒ shì tā xīn zhōng de bǎo
 wǒ yào zàn měi wǒ yào huān xiào zhǔ zuì zhī dào wǒ de xū yào
 bù zài yōu chóu wán quán xìn kào yīn zhǔ gào sù wǒ tā dōu zhī dào
 yīn zhǔ gào sù wǒ tā dōu zhī dào</lyrics>
<title>zhǔ zuì zhī dào wǒ de xū yào 迦南1329</title>
</song>